{"tid":407761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真係笑話系列] 煞無赦","createTime":"2017-09-20T16:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T14:17:17.000Z","uid":34144,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8734c036d5b92455096076bd586e46125ee5d8d7","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"話說有日君堯同個女喺街到見到個阿婆亂過媽路，就想阻止佢。 <br />\n<br />\n點知君堯未出聲，個女就指住個阿婆大大聲叫：「阿婆你亂過馬路，殺無赦!」 <br />\n<br />\n君堯當堂嚇咗一跳，就問：「阿囡，婆婆亂過馬路姐，唔洗殺無赦咁激進掛？」 <br />\n<br />\n阿女就即刻駁嘴：「老豆，唔係『殺』無赦，係『煞』無赦啊！即係一定要煞停佢啊！」 <br />\n<br />\n君堯：^*(&amp;&amp;&amp;(#($%#%$ON(( <br />\n<br />\n感謝讀者何匪君提供笑話，將聯絡送上「真係笑話-煞梨全加」一本致謝，如你有笑話，歡迎電郵給我：fuckyouhogwanjiu@gmail.com"},{"pid":"9919b3563ea29c4de396f61a623248633da437d8","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb3171bed054ce59f0486473bcb02bb87c991f9","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:34:02.000Z","msg":"昨日笑話,今日香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0252c8e83cade7debbafb519db63a8b59c12f41c","tid":407761,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"呢個幾得"},{"pid":"51a6205a3d3d86c8235defafbe6d2b94d9d5d9c6","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個幾得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅字為笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc30723c92211d06630f3f10c1d95fbf5cf055ef","tid":407761,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"即刻駁嘴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b172118ee1cb4c1343da841414cf37fba81a0c53","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"好想被何生瘋狂煞無赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20ebc880749c7e5e446603b6ca684caee3122ac","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:53:34.000Z","msg":"快啲煞我啦，煞啊，煞啦，仲唔煞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac143edff44ba42b8e48abb274b46e5b08f817a1","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"本身是律師的立法會議員何君堯，周日（16日）在集會上發表倡「港獨」者「殺無赦」的言論。繼昨日凌晨於臉書上澄清，「殺」的意思只是「煞停他們渲染港獨的違法言論」後，何君堯今日出席活動再次回應，強調當時的意思只是「煞停港獨」，希望外界不要繼續糾纏。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道，何君堯今日回應事件時，對社會有不同解讀感遺憾，認為可能是他當日的用字不理想所致，強調不是煽動他人犯法或提倡殺人。不過，何君堯認為無需收回有關言論，亦不擔心會遭到刑事起訴，自己是憑良心出發且遵守《基本法》。另外他亦提到，對於有人事件在網上以語言暴力、網絡欺凌方式出言針對他及其家人，他會聯絡警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n香港律師會今日已證實接獲有關何君堯的投訴，律師會早前表示，如接獲會員投訴，將按既定程序保密處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://post852.com/229880/何君堯重申「殺」為「煞停港獨」　擬要求警方跟/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpost852.com%2F229880%2F%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E3%80%8C%E6%AE%BA%E3%80%8D%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8C%E7%85%9E%E5%81%9C%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E6%93%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%B7%9F%2F&d=Saleply5TRv7NA95VFOxyb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ea0bae9e\" target=\"_blank\">post852.com/229880/何君堯重申「殺」為「煞停港獨」　擬要求警方跟/</a>"},{"pid":"dbddea20067ba79b3263cc47036802fd173014a1","tid":407761,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"五毛狗，煞無赦！"},{"pid":"63659c6f08fdcbe933b6d5b6afc565e049716774","tid":407761,"uid":15793,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:26:05.000Z","msg":"呢個點睇：<br />\n<br />\n君堯阿女肚痾，君堯：「殺無赦!」阿女：「老豆，肚唔駛死下話？」老豆：「煞！無瀉！煞停D屎，無肚瀉。」阿女：「;)&amp;&amp;(;:&amp;!」"},{"pid":"b9e957d4df351beb2bb3e20e77bbd887872c577f","tid":407761,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:02:54.000Z","msg":"阿女叫君如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacf63bce99232a89f25f2091c289e45bf85a3b2","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"而家何匪話佢連殺都冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed2c2cc9ecd82e598d35d12d9f4fb2fd866af95","tid":407761,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf2144dafcd9fce11a4c4fa463faa4bb3a1b7be","tid":407761,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"煞無赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}